deftms ~>>>UNION 'identification of vertices of an union of PLSVO
from NBOBUN PLSVO of numbered vertices from 1 up to NS(i) 
the array NDSCOU points on the last vertex of each PLSVO
  ( NDSCOU(0)=0 , NDSCOU(i)=sum( NS(j) ) j=1,i )
the array NOSOUN gives the number of each vertex of each PLSVO in the
numbering after the identification of common vertices of the PLSVO'
variable muet DATE 'date of creation of the TMS' reel2  ;
variable muet NUTD 'number of the descriptor array TD' entier ; 
variable NBOBUN   'number of PLSVO of the union'  entier ;
tableau  NDSCOU(0..NBOBUN) 'pointer on the last vertex of each PLSVO' entier ;
tableau  NUSOUN(1..NDSCOU(NBOBUN)) 'numbers of vertices in the union' entier ;
tableau  NDTCOU(0..NBOBUN) 'pointer on the last TG of each PLSVO'  entier ;
tableau  NUTGUN(1..NDTCOU(NBOBUN)) 'numbers of TG in the union' entier ;
fintms ;
